1
00:00:07,302 --> 00:00:08,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Hyun Woo who lives across the street...</font>

2
00:00:12,732 --> 00:00:13,972
<font color=#FFFF00>is my real brother.</font>

3
00:00:14,772 --> 00:00:15,802
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

4
00:00:23,102 --> 00:00:24,132
<font color=#FFFF00>I am...</font>

5
00:00:26,732 --> 00:00:28,632
<font color=#FFFF00>the son of the driver who committed suicide.</font>

6
00:00:31,802 --> 00:00:33,032
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm Lee Sang Woo.</font>

7
00:00:35,172 --> 00:00:36,332
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

8
00:01:00,002 --> 00:01:01,272
<font color=#FFFF00>(Episode 41)</font>

9
00:01:11,032 --> 00:01:14,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Now everything makes sense.</font>

10
00:01:15,842 --> 00:01:17,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

11
00:01:19,602 --> 00:01:21,202
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what to say.</font>

12
00:01:22,632 --> 00:01:23,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyung Seop,</font>

13
00:01:24,672 --> 00:01:26,332
<font color=#FFFF00>don't you have a mother?</font>

14
00:01:28,172 --> 00:01:30,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you have a wife? Why did you do that?</font>

15
00:01:31,902 --> 00:01:33,832
<font color=#FFFF00>You could've discussed it with us.</font>

16
00:01:34,532 --> 00:01:36,402
<font color=#FFFF00>If Seong Joon didn't tell us,</font>

17
00:01:36,532 --> 00:01:40,402
<font color=#FFFF00>were you going to carry the burden alone for the rest of your life?</font>

18
00:01:42,372 --> 00:01:43,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

19
00:01:44,802 --> 00:01:45,902
<font color=#FFFF00>Even now,</font>

20
00:01:46,902 --> 00:01:50,532
<font color=#FFFF00>I think I should've carried the burden alone.</font>

21
00:01:50,932 --> 00:01:52,332
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you say?</font>

22
00:01:52,972 --> 00:01:54,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Ae.</font>

23
00:01:54,472 --> 00:01:57,272
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you lie to me like this?</font>

24
00:01:57,832 --> 00:01:59,872
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you make me raise the son of...</font>

25
00:01:59,872 --> 00:02:01,402
<font color=#FFFF00>that driver?</font>

26
00:02:01,802 --> 00:02:03,532
<font color=#FFFF00>And you tore my heart by...</font>

27
00:02:03,532 --> 00:02:05,072
<font color=#FFFF00>lying that you had an affair.</font>

28
00:02:07,102 --> 00:02:09,332
<font color=#FFFF00>If I told you the truth,</font>

29
00:02:10,002 --> 00:02:11,972
<font color=#FFFF00>would you have raised Seong Joon?</font>

30
00:02:12,002 --> 00:02:14,132
<font color=#FFFF00>I certainly wouldn't have. Why would I raise him?</font>

31
00:02:14,242 --> 00:02:16,802
<font color=#FFFF00>- Did I kill the bus driver? - Even if that's the case,</font>

32
00:02:18,502 --> 00:02:21,572
<font color=#FFFF00>this is no way to treat your wife with whom you lived all your life.</font>

33
00:02:22,242 --> 00:02:23,932
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway,</font>

34
00:02:24,472 --> 00:02:26,172
<font color=#FFFF00>it's Jeong Ae who raised Seong Joon.</font>

35
00:02:27,872 --> 00:02:31,172
<font color=#FFFF00>It took years for her to accept him as her son.</font>

36
00:02:32,202 --> 00:02:35,242
<font color=#FFFF00>At the end, she raised him well.</font>

37
00:02:35,872 --> 00:02:37,742
<font color=#FFFF00>Then you should have at least...</font>

38
00:02:37,802 --> 00:02:39,302
<font color=#FFFF00>told her...</font>

39
00:02:39,742 --> 00:02:42,002
<font color=#FFFF00>who she is raising...</font>

40
00:02:42,002 --> 00:02:44,872
<font color=#FFFF00>and from where you brought him.</font>

41
00:02:44,872 --> 00:02:46,002
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what marriage is.</font>

42
00:02:47,502 --> 00:02:48,732
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

43
00:02:50,802 --> 00:02:54,232
<font color=#FFFF00>I was worried if I told her, Seong Joon wouldn't grow up well.</font>

44
00:02:54,902 --> 00:02:56,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother.</font>

45
00:02:57,072 --> 00:02:59,332
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you hear what he just said?</font>

46
00:03:00,372 --> 00:03:03,072
<font color=#FFFF00>A poor man ended his life after all.</font>

47
00:03:03,372 --> 00:03:05,302
<font color=#FFFF00>He left his children behind.</font>

48
00:03:05,872 --> 00:03:08,472
<font color=#FFFF00>I couldn't turn my eyes away from them.</font>

49
00:03:08,702 --> 00:03:11,432
<font color=#FFFF00>You should have brought both of them and raised them.</font>

50
00:03:11,472 --> 00:03:14,172
<font color=#FFFF00>If you did, this disaster wouldn't have happened now.</font>

51
00:03:14,632 --> 00:03:16,632
<font color=#FFFF00>I wanted to do that too.</font>

52
00:03:16,832 --> 00:03:19,972
<font color=#FFFF00>When I went to get him, he was already adopted and left Korea.</font>

53
00:03:20,402 --> 00:03:21,472
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

54
00:03:22,202 --> 00:03:23,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

55
00:03:24,232 --> 00:03:26,202
<font color=#FFFF00>This is unbelievable.</font>

56
00:03:27,402 --> 00:03:29,432
<font color=#FFFF00>What I have committed is quite grave, Mom.</font>

57
00:03:32,302 --> 00:03:33,532
<font color=#FFFF00>Back then,</font>

58
00:03:34,572 --> 00:03:36,432
<font color=#FFFF00>I only cared about my children.</font>

59
00:03:37,832 --> 00:03:39,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway,</font>

60
00:03:40,932 --> 00:03:43,902
<font color=#FFFF00>you must have gone through a very difficult time all these years.</font>

61
00:03:45,102 --> 00:03:46,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother.</font>

62
00:03:47,132 --> 00:03:48,602
<font color=#FFFF00>What about preposterous feelings I have?</font>

63
00:03:49,272 --> 00:03:51,172
<font color=#FFFF00>I just found out that I have been raising...</font>

64
00:03:51,202 --> 00:03:54,432
<font color=#FFFF00>the son of the bus driver who committed suicide for 23 years.</font>

65
00:03:55,102 --> 00:03:58,402
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't ever understand you.</font>

66
00:03:58,472 --> 00:03:59,902
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't forgive you.</font>

67
00:04:04,602 --> 00:04:05,602
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

68
00:04:06,972 --> 00:04:09,902
<font color=#FFFF00>How will we resolve this problem now?</font>

69
00:04:15,502 --> 00:04:17,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you do it?</font>

70
00:04:17,832 --> 00:04:18,872
<font color=#FFFF00>If I don't,</font>

71
00:04:19,632 --> 00:04:21,332
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad and you will get hurt.</font>

72
00:04:21,672 --> 00:04:22,672
<font color=#FFFF00>What about you?</font>

73
00:04:24,172 --> 00:04:27,042
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't keep this a secret forever.</font>

74
00:04:27,902 --> 00:04:29,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Things are already happening.</font>

75
00:04:33,902 --> 00:04:35,972
<font color=#FFFF00>What will we do from now on?</font>

76
00:04:36,972 --> 00:04:39,132
<font color=#FFFF00>All we have left is getting kicked out. Is that it?</font>

77
00:04:42,772 --> 00:04:44,172
<font color=#FFFF00>You. Han Seong Joon!</font>

78
00:04:46,072 --> 00:04:47,602
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you just sit here?</font>

79
00:04:49,332 --> 00:04:50,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa.</font>

80
00:04:52,102 --> 00:04:54,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Go to that jerk, Lee Hyun Woo...</font>

81
00:04:54,132 --> 00:04:55,572
<font color=#FFFF00>and tell him to find my brother, Seong Hoon.</font>

82
00:04:55,802 --> 00:04:58,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell him to get our house back this instant!</font>

83
00:04:59,042 --> 00:05:00,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa. Stop it.</font>

84
00:05:00,872 --> 00:05:03,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa. Stop it. Stop!</font>

85
00:05:03,772 --> 00:05:06,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell him to pay the monetary penalty Seong Sik paid.</font>

86
00:05:07,632 --> 00:05:10,432
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you just sit here and do nothing?</font>

87
00:05:10,632 --> 00:05:13,072
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you stay in this house?</font>

88
00:05:13,272 --> 00:05:15,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa. You can't treat him like this.</font>

89
00:05:16,002 --> 00:05:17,932
<font color=#FFFF00>This isn't Seong Joon's fault.</font>

90
00:05:17,932 --> 00:05:19,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Why isn't it his fault?</font>

91
00:05:19,542 --> 00:05:21,372
<font color=#FFFF00>He is Lee Hyun Woo's brother!</font>

92
00:05:21,432 --> 00:05:22,502
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa.</font>

93
00:05:22,972 --> 00:05:24,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, that's enough.</font>

94
00:05:24,802 --> 00:05:25,872
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hey. - If you are his brother,</font>

95
00:05:25,872 --> 00:05:28,302
<font color=#FFFF00>shouldn't you take full responsibility for this disaster?</font>

96
00:05:28,472 --> 00:05:29,602
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know...</font>

97
00:05:30,172 --> 00:05:33,132
<font color=#FFFF00>for how long we fed, clothed, and raised you?</font>

98
00:05:33,402 --> 00:05:35,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Is this how you repay our kindness?</font>

99
00:05:35,702 --> 00:05:37,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, Jeong Hwa. Come on.</font>

100
00:05:37,372 --> 00:05:39,672
<font color=#FFFF00>- You. Come out now. Come out! - You...</font>

101
00:05:39,672 --> 00:05:41,632
<font color=#FFFF00>- Let go of me. - Come out!</font>

102
00:05:41,702 --> 00:05:44,032
<font color=#FFFF00>Go to your brother! You, jerk.</font>

103
00:05:44,402 --> 00:05:46,502
<font color=#FFFF00>Look at him. He's doing nothing.</font>

104
00:05:51,802 --> 00:05:54,302
<font color=#FFFF00>- Let me go. I'm not done with him. - Goodness.</font>

105
00:05:54,302 --> 00:05:56,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it! Be quiet!</font>

106
00:05:57,132 --> 00:05:59,672
<font color=#FFFF00>How can a girl be so strong?</font>

107
00:05:59,832 --> 00:06:02,872
<font color=#FFFF00>You are as loud as a train too!</font>

108
00:06:03,972 --> 00:06:05,932
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you bring her here?</font>

109
00:06:06,172 --> 00:06:08,802
<font color=#FFFF00>What was I supposed to do?</font>

110
00:06:08,972 --> 00:06:10,402
<font color=#FFFF00>If I leave her on the second floor,</font>

111
00:06:10,532 --> 00:06:12,632
<font color=#FFFF00>she might end up beating up Seong Joon.</font>

112
00:06:12,672 --> 00:06:14,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think that's the only thing I'll do?</font>

113
00:06:14,832 --> 00:06:16,832
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't let that sibling off easy.</font>

114
00:06:17,002 --> 00:06:19,472
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa! Can't you be quiet?</font>

115
00:06:21,672 --> 00:06:24,872
<font color=#FFFF00>The midterm week will start the day after tomorrow for our children.</font>

116
00:06:25,032 --> 00:06:26,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you going to keep this up?</font>

117
00:06:27,272 --> 00:06:28,832
<font color=#FFFF00>Please keep it down!</font>

118
00:06:35,202 --> 00:06:36,272
<font color=#FFFF00>This is the first...</font>

119
00:06:36,802 --> 00:06:38,732
<font color=#FFFF00>midterm in their third year of middle school.</font>

120
00:06:38,972 --> 00:06:41,972
<font color=#FFFF00>If you keep this up and they don't do well on their exams,</font>

121
00:06:42,502 --> 00:06:43,802
<font color=#FFFF00>are you going to be held responsible?</font>

122
00:06:44,372 --> 00:06:46,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, Hee Sook.</font>

123
00:06:47,602 --> 00:06:50,732
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you talk about their education when our house is ruined?</font>

124
00:06:51,032 --> 00:06:53,902
<font color=#FFFF00>If I don't talk about their education,</font>

125
00:06:54,672 --> 00:06:56,202
<font color=#FFFF00>what would I talk about?</font>

126
00:06:56,972 --> 00:07:00,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Should I badmouth Father who has suffered all these years...</font>

127
00:07:00,302 --> 00:07:02,602
<font color=#FFFF00>by bringing up what happened 23 years ago?</font>

128
00:07:02,602 --> 00:07:04,602
<font color=#FFFF00>Or should I come up with a plan about Seong Joon...</font>

129
00:07:04,602 --> 00:07:07,002
<font color=#FFFF00>who lost his family and grew up uncomfortably.</font>

130
00:07:07,072 --> 00:07:08,902
<font color=#FFFF00>Or should I...</font>

131
00:07:09,232 --> 00:07:12,172
<font color=#FFFF00>talk about our wretched feelings...</font>

132
00:07:12,972 --> 00:07:14,172
<font color=#FFFF00>at Hye Joo...</font>

133
00:07:14,402 --> 00:07:17,272
<font color=#FFFF00>whose husband, Seong Hoon...</font>

134
00:07:17,272 --> 00:07:19,502
<font color=#FFFF00>ruined our family?</font>

135
00:07:19,502 --> 00:07:22,072
<font color=#FFFF00>Should I do that instead?</font>

136
00:07:22,372 --> 00:07:24,902
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh. Sit down.</font>

137
00:07:27,472 --> 00:07:29,232
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo.</font>

138
00:07:29,872 --> 00:07:31,502
<font color=#FFFF00>You haven't heard from Seong Hoon yet?</font>

139
00:07:32,772 --> 00:07:33,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Not yet.</font>

140
00:07:34,902 --> 00:07:36,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Should I go out and look for him?</font>

141
00:07:37,302 --> 00:07:39,632
<font color=#FFFF00>What if he committed suicide somewhere?</font>

142
00:07:39,802 --> 00:07:41,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo.</font>

143
00:07:41,302 --> 00:07:44,232
<font color=#FFFF00>How many times have I told you to take care of your husband?</font>

144
00:07:44,402 --> 00:07:46,032
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon is a softie.</font>

145
00:07:46,032 --> 00:07:48,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you know that he lives well when he's being taken care of...</font>

146
00:07:48,432 --> 00:07:50,572
<font color=#FFFF00>after spending all these years with him?</font>

147
00:07:51,102 --> 00:07:53,702
<font color=#FFFF00>How bad were you taking care of him to cause this mess?</font>

148
00:07:53,702 --> 00:07:54,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Exactly.</font>

149
00:07:55,932 --> 00:07:58,572
<font color=#FFFF00>I think I should report to the police.</font>

150
00:07:58,732 --> 00:08:00,272
<font color=#FFFF00>I agree.</font>

151
00:08:00,572 --> 00:08:03,672
<font color=#FFFF00>We should report to the police. They will form a search party for him.</font>

152
00:08:04,572 --> 00:08:05,972
<font color=#FFFF00>I mean...</font>

153
00:08:05,972 --> 00:08:08,772
<font color=#FFFF00>if he moved into the house to take care of Father,</font>

154
00:08:08,772 --> 00:08:12,032
<font color=#FFFF00>he should have done that. How could he...</font>

155
00:08:12,032 --> 00:08:14,402
<font color=#FFFF00>lose Father's house overnight?</font>

156
00:08:14,602 --> 00:08:16,032
<font color=#FFFF00>What does this house mean to him?</font>

157
00:08:16,032 --> 00:08:19,372
<font color=#FFFF00>This house is the only inheritance...</font>

158
00:08:19,532 --> 00:08:21,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother and Father will pass on to us. Am I wrong?</font>

159
00:08:21,932 --> 00:08:25,272
<font color=#FFFF00>How could he single-handedly lose...</font>

160
00:08:25,272 --> 00:08:28,272
<font color=#FFFF00>this house without talking to us first?</font>

161
00:08:28,802 --> 00:08:31,532
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's send out a search party for him and catch him.</font>

162
00:08:31,602 --> 00:08:33,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook.</font>

163
00:08:37,172 --> 00:08:39,432
<font color=#FFFF00>Was that how you were feeling, Hee Sook?</font>

164
00:08:39,902 --> 00:08:42,232
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes, it was. - What?</font>

165
00:08:42,402 --> 00:08:44,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Seriously. Stop it.</font>

166
00:08:44,432 --> 00:08:47,142
<font color=#FFFF00>We have to find Seong Hoon by all means.</font>

167
00:08:48,472 --> 00:08:50,072
<font color=#FFFF00>Since he is weak-minded,</font>

168
00:08:50,602 --> 00:08:51,872
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what will happen to him...</font>

169
00:08:53,102 --> 00:08:55,772
<font color=#FFFF00>once he starts thinking of doing something stupid.</font>

170
00:08:57,102 --> 00:09:00,642
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do these incompetent oldest sons hide...</font>

171
00:09:00,642 --> 00:09:02,702
<font color=#FFFF00>after they ruin their businesses...</font>

172
00:09:02,802 --> 00:09:04,602
<font color=#FFFF00>and the whole family?</font>

173
00:09:04,802 --> 00:09:06,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do they hide?</font>

174
00:09:06,142 --> 00:09:09,272
<font color=#FFFF00>They ought to go out and try to solve this mess.</font>

175
00:09:09,932 --> 00:09:10,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey.</font>

176
00:09:11,602 --> 00:09:13,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't be so cruel.</font>

177
00:09:14,032 --> 00:09:15,572
<font color=#FFFF00>He's still my brother.</font>

178
00:09:15,732 --> 00:09:18,642
<font color=#FFFF00>We are about to end up on the streets. How can you say that?</font>

179
00:09:22,102 --> 00:09:24,472
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo. Where are you going?</font>

180
00:09:25,302 --> 00:09:26,772
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to go out.</font>

181
00:09:27,302 --> 00:09:30,232
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hye Joo. Let me go with you. - All right.</font>

182
00:09:30,402 --> 00:09:31,532
<font color=#FFFF00>Seriously!</font>

183
00:09:31,972 --> 00:09:33,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo. Hye Joo!</font>

184
00:09:35,202 --> 00:09:37,642
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe them.</font>

185
00:09:39,732 --> 00:09:40,732
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

186
00:09:55,532 --> 00:09:56,532
<font color=#FFFF00>This can't...</font>

187
00:10:00,002 --> 00:10:01,142
<font color=#FFFF00>be happening.</font>

188
00:10:50,102 --> 00:10:51,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Why?</font>

189
00:10:52,002 --> 00:10:55,272
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you go for a run because you were feeling frustrated?</font>

190
00:10:56,602 --> 00:11:00,272
<font color=#FFFF00>I mean you did completely destroy a happy family.</font>

191
00:11:00,332 --> 00:11:02,072
<font color=#FFFF00>You must be if you are a human being.</font>

192
00:11:02,832 --> 00:11:04,232
<font color=#FFFF00>You seem furious.</font>

193
00:11:04,302 --> 00:11:06,302
<font color=#FFFF00>The problem at your family must have gotten quite serious then.</font>

194
00:11:14,472 --> 00:11:16,272
<font color=#FFFF00>Is this what you wanted?</font>

195
00:11:16,732 --> 00:11:18,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know what condition Seong Joon is in?</font>

196
00:11:21,232 --> 00:11:24,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, I suppose he's still pretending to be their family.</font>

197
00:11:24,302 --> 00:11:25,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, Hyun Woo.</font>

198
00:11:26,172 --> 00:11:27,902
<font color=#FFFF00>Everything is over.</font>

199
00:11:28,372 --> 00:11:31,132
<font color=#FFFF00>He covered up what you and my uncle did.</font>

200
00:11:31,502 --> 00:11:34,532
<font color=#FFFF00>He covered for me who once foolishly loved you.</font>

201
00:11:34,632 --> 00:11:36,902
<font color=#FFFF00>He took all the blame by himself. Did you know that?</font>

202
00:11:38,202 --> 00:11:39,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you have to do this?</font>

203
00:11:40,302 --> 00:11:43,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Does Seong Joon have to be hated and kicked out by his family?</font>

204
00:11:44,032 --> 00:11:46,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Will that put an end to your revenge?</font>

205
00:11:46,572 --> 00:11:49,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Who is the victim of this revenge?</font>

206
00:11:50,002 --> 00:11:51,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Is my family the victim?</font>

207
00:11:51,372 --> 00:11:53,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think you and Seong Joon are the victims?</font>

208
00:11:56,172 --> 00:11:57,832
<font color=#FFFF00>What on earth happened?</font>

209
00:11:58,102 --> 00:11:59,232
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon...</font>

210
00:12:00,172 --> 00:12:02,132
<font color=#FFFF00>kneeled down in front of my family...</font>

211
00:12:02,732 --> 00:12:04,972
<font color=#FFFF00>and asked for forgiveness of what you did...</font>

212
00:12:05,572 --> 00:12:07,572
<font color=#FFFF00>saying that it was all his fault.</font>

213
00:12:09,272 --> 00:12:11,472
<font color=#FFFF00>After my family lost jobs and honor, they couldn't keep a cool head.</font>

214
00:12:11,602 --> 00:12:14,672
<font color=#FFFF00>He let them give him a hard time.</font>

215
00:12:15,072 --> 00:12:17,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that really what you wanted?</font>

216
00:12:18,472 --> 00:12:19,602
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a pathetic jerk.</font>

217
00:12:22,402 --> 00:12:23,502
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

218
00:12:25,032 --> 00:12:27,172
<font color=#FFFF00>You are such a bad person.</font>

219
00:12:28,072 --> 00:12:30,572
<font color=#FFFF00>You only care about yourself.</font>

220
00:12:31,032 --> 00:12:34,232
<font color=#FFFF00>You are a self-obsessed person who never cares about other people.</font>

221
00:12:35,472 --> 00:12:37,002
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you the other day.</font>

222
00:12:37,632 --> 00:12:39,702
<font color=#FFFF00>That I'm not a good person.</font>

223
00:12:40,602 --> 00:12:43,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Did I ever tried to hide that I'm a bad person?</font>

224
00:12:46,332 --> 00:12:48,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. You are right.</font>

225
00:12:49,732 --> 00:12:51,702
<font color=#FFFF00>I just forgot that.</font>

226
00:12:56,572 --> 00:12:57,702
<font color=#FFFF00>I will never forget...</font>

227
00:12:58,472 --> 00:13:00,032
<font color=#FFFF00>the lesson you taught me today.</font>

228
00:13:01,502 --> 00:13:02,872
<font color=#FFFF00>I've tried to think...</font>

229
00:13:03,372 --> 00:13:05,932
<font color=#FFFF00>that you are doing all this because you are hurt.</font>

230
00:13:06,672 --> 00:13:07,872
<font color=#FFFF00>I wanted...</font>

231
00:13:08,272 --> 00:13:10,502
<font color=#FFFF00>to help you heal your broken heart.</font>

232
00:13:10,802 --> 00:13:13,472
<font color=#FFFF00>I've held out with that thought in mind.</font>

233
00:13:15,832 --> 00:13:17,372
<font color=#FFFF00>I should probably thank you.</font>

234
00:13:17,732 --> 00:13:21,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Thanks to you, I can finally let go of it and move on.</font>

235
00:13:29,072 --> 00:13:31,172
<font color=#FFFF00>Take care, Hyun Woo.</font>

236
00:13:32,872 --> 00:13:34,672
<font color=#FFFF00>I will leave...</font>

237
00:13:36,102 --> 00:13:37,972
<font color=#FFFF00>all my feelings for you here.</font>

238
00:13:39,172 --> 00:13:41,832
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's never see each other again.</font>

239
00:14:02,402 --> 00:14:04,102
<font color=#FFFF00>What a jerk.</font>

240
00:14:04,432 --> 00:14:07,072
<font color=#FFFF00>He doesn't even know how much I loved him.</font>

241
00:14:09,072 --> 00:14:11,532
<font color=#FFFF00>This is the last time I'll ever come here!</font>

242
00:14:40,102 --> 00:14:42,272
<font color=#FFFF00>The mortgage on the building of...</font>

243
00:14:42,272 --> 00:14:43,732
<font color=#FFFF00>57-17, Bangbae-dong...</font>

244
00:14:44,172 --> 00:14:45,832
<font color=#FFFF00>It is 1.5 million dollars.</font>

245
00:14:45,902 --> 00:14:46,972
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

246
00:14:47,172 --> 00:14:49,702
<font color=#FFFF00>He borrowed as much money as he could.</font>

247
00:14:49,802 --> 00:14:51,932
<font color=#FFFF00>The term of redemption is 30 years.</font>

248
00:14:52,132 --> 00:14:55,972
<font color=#FFFF00>You should repay the principal and interest from the end of the month.</font>

249
00:14:56,102 --> 00:14:58,402
<font color=#FFFF00>The interest rate will change every three months.</font>

250
00:14:58,602 --> 00:15:01,502
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a large sum of money.</font>

251
00:15:01,702 --> 00:15:04,272
<font color=#FFFF00>If the principal and interest are past due over two months,</font>

252
00:15:04,432 --> 00:15:07,172
<font color=#FFFF00>the bank may foreclose on your house.</font>

253
00:15:08,072 --> 00:15:10,272
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - They may attach your property.</font>

254
00:15:14,732 --> 00:15:16,872
<font color=#FFFF00>He just arrived at the office.</font>

255
00:15:16,872 --> 00:15:19,232
<font color=#FFFF00>Why does he look so serious?</font>

256
00:15:19,632 --> 00:15:21,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Maybe he can't reach Dong Hui.</font>

257
00:15:25,172 --> 00:15:28,772
<font color=#FFFF00>If things go like this, our drama will be canceled.</font>

258
00:15:30,102 --> 00:15:31,532
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe this.</font>

259
00:15:31,932 --> 00:15:34,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Why is it so hard to air a drama?</font>

260
00:15:35,472 --> 00:15:38,002
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with Director Han by the way?</font>

261
00:15:38,072 --> 00:15:40,702
<font color=#FFFF00>I know. Writer Choi and Dong Hui...</font>

262
00:15:40,702 --> 00:15:42,402
<font color=#FFFF00>are so irresponsible.</font>

263
00:15:42,772 --> 00:15:44,802
<font color=#FFFF00>We don't know it yet.</font>

264
00:15:44,832 --> 00:15:46,702
<font color=#FFFF00>We still have some time left.</font>

265
00:15:46,702 --> 00:15:48,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Whatever.</font>

266
00:15:48,702 --> 00:15:49,832
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

267
00:15:54,602 --> 00:15:56,932
<font color=#FFFF00>What? That's ridiculous.</font>

268
00:15:56,972 --> 00:15:57,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Why would he close them?</font>

269
00:16:19,572 --> 00:16:22,332
<font color=#FFFF00>This is Director Han from Contents Marketing Department.</font>

270
00:16:22,732 --> 00:16:26,202
<font color=#FFFF00>I'd like to cash in retirement fund prematurely.</font>

271
00:16:26,972 --> 00:16:28,432
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it possible?</font>

272
00:16:30,772 --> 00:16:31,802
<font color=#FFFF00>All right.</font>

273
00:16:32,902 --> 00:16:36,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Can I also apply for an employees loan?</font>

274
00:16:39,772 --> 00:16:40,772
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

275
00:16:42,372 --> 00:16:44,702
<font color=#FFFF00>I will visit as soon as the documents are ready.</font>

276
00:16:46,032 --> 00:16:47,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

277
00:16:57,572 --> 00:16:59,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Please let me out.</font>

278
00:16:59,732 --> 00:17:01,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me out.</font>

279
00:17:03,002 --> 00:17:04,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

280
00:17:04,202 --> 00:17:07,432
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me see my grandmother.</font>

281
00:17:08,672 --> 00:17:09,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey.</font>

282
00:17:10,272 --> 00:17:12,072
<font color=#FFFF00>Is anyone there?</font>

283
00:17:17,272 --> 00:17:18,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on out.</font>

284
00:17:31,972 --> 00:17:33,072
<font color=#FFFF00>You should eat.</font>

285
00:17:33,302 --> 00:17:35,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Chairman Bang and Director Bang are out.</font>

286
00:17:38,772 --> 00:17:39,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

287
00:17:48,872 --> 00:17:51,272
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. She's having breakfast.</font>

288
00:17:52,002 --> 00:17:53,102
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a little late.</font>

289
00:17:54,872 --> 00:17:56,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. I'll be right there.</font>

290
00:18:11,232 --> 00:18:12,232
<font color=#FFFF00>What is this?</font>

291
00:18:12,732 --> 00:18:14,072
<font color=#FFFF00>This is a gift from Chairman Bang.</font>

292
00:18:17,172 --> 00:18:19,232
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't use the internet with it though.</font>

293
00:18:36,672 --> 00:18:37,702
<font color=#FFFF00>It's me.</font>

294
00:18:38,102 --> 00:18:39,932
<font color=#FFFF00>What is Dong Hui doing now?</font>

295
00:18:39,932 --> 00:18:42,632
<font color=#FFFF00>She just had breakfast and went back to her room.</font>

296
00:18:42,732 --> 00:18:44,102
<font color=#FFFF00>She ate breakfast?</font>

297
00:18:44,702 --> 00:18:46,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. And she got...</font>

298
00:18:46,372 --> 00:18:48,702
<font color=#FFFF00>a new laptop today.</font>

299
00:18:50,842 --> 00:18:51,902
<font color=#FFFF00>All right.</font>

300
00:18:56,232 --> 00:18:57,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Where on earth is Dong Hui?</font>

301
00:18:58,402 --> 00:18:59,472
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry, sir.</font>

302
00:19:00,202 --> 00:19:02,872
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you to keep an eye on her.</font>

303
00:19:03,772 --> 00:19:05,842
<font color=#FFFF00>It seems she just left last night.</font>

304
00:19:07,432 --> 00:19:08,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Go find her.</font>

305
00:19:09,472 --> 00:19:10,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Without Dong Hui,</font>

306
00:19:11,342 --> 00:19:13,602
<font color=#FFFF00>I will never get the will from her.</font>

307
00:19:13,772 --> 00:19:16,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Go find Dong Hui as soon as possible.</font>

308
00:19:28,132 --> 00:19:30,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Right. What is Dong Hui doing?</font>

309
00:19:30,802 --> 00:19:31,932
<font color=#FFFF00>She's at home.</font>

310
00:19:32,272 --> 00:19:33,672
<font color=#FFFF00>And I gave her the laptop.</font>

311
00:19:34,302 --> 00:19:35,302
<font color=#FFFF00>All right.</font>

312
00:19:36,702 --> 00:19:38,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you call the sanatorium?</font>

313
00:19:38,302 --> 00:19:41,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. I told them we'll be there in two hours.</font>

314
00:19:41,432 --> 00:19:42,902
<font color=#FFFF00>What about Gui Boon?</font>

315
00:19:43,572 --> 00:19:45,102
<font color=#FFFF00>She hasn't called me yet.</font>

316
00:19:45,432 --> 00:19:46,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you cancel the meeting?</font>

317
00:19:47,072 --> 00:19:48,402
<font color=#FFFF00>It's pushed back to tomorrow.</font>

318
00:19:48,772 --> 00:19:50,132
<font color=#FFFF00>All right. Let's go.</font>

319
00:20:50,672 --> 00:20:54,232
<font color=#FFFF00>(Hearty Sanatorium)</font>

320
00:20:59,372 --> 00:21:02,072
<font color=#FFFF00>(Hearty Sanatorium)</font>

321
00:21:02,072 --> 00:21:03,602
<font color=#FFFF00>What is this place?</font>

322
00:21:04,342 --> 00:21:06,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Hearty Sanatorium?</font>

323
00:21:07,472 --> 00:21:11,302
<font color=#FFFF00>(Hearty Sanatorium)</font>

324
00:21:24,772 --> 00:21:27,502
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know what this is?</font>

325
00:21:32,702 --> 00:21:34,602
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the DNA test results...</font>

326
00:21:35,202 --> 00:21:37,002
<font color=#FFFF00>of Hyun Jeong.</font>

327
00:21:39,972 --> 00:21:43,172
<font color=#FFFF00>Why didn't I figure it out sooner?</font>

328
00:21:43,972 --> 00:21:45,032
<font color=#FFFF00>Now that I think of it,</font>

329
00:21:46,672 --> 00:21:49,032
<font color=#FFFF00>she looks just like her mother.</font>

330
00:21:49,472 --> 00:21:51,402
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not just her face.</font>

331
00:21:52,302 --> 00:21:54,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Even her character is the same as her mother's.</font>

332
00:21:59,232 --> 00:22:01,272
<font color=#FFFF00>She's locked up in my house.</font>

333
00:22:02,102 --> 00:22:05,532
<font color=#FFFF00>She keeps making a fuss screaming and yelling.</font>

334
00:22:08,132 --> 00:22:09,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you really...</font>

335
00:22:11,402 --> 00:22:12,902
<font color=#FFFF00>have to do all this?</font>

336
00:22:33,172 --> 00:22:34,432
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother?</font>

337
00:22:39,572 --> 00:22:40,902
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why...</font>

338
00:22:41,402 --> 00:22:44,872
<font color=#FFFF00>you should've done my favor in the first place.</font>

339
00:22:45,372 --> 00:22:47,602
<font color=#FFFF00>Then I wouldn't have wasted such a long time.</font>

340
00:22:48,472 --> 00:22:51,132
<font color=#FFFF00>And you also wouldn't have had to spend...</font>

341
00:22:51,532 --> 00:22:52,972
<font color=#FFFF00>a lonely life...</font>

342
00:22:53,332 --> 00:22:56,272
<font color=#FFFF00>in this room like now.</font>

343
00:22:56,832 --> 00:22:59,472
<font color=#FFFF00>You are the worst son the world has ever known.</font>

344
00:23:00,972 --> 00:23:04,302
<font color=#FFFF00>It's really humiliating to hear you...</font>

345
00:23:04,332 --> 00:23:06,432
<font color=#FFFF00>call me mother.</font>

346
00:23:08,072 --> 00:23:11,072
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel exactly the same.</font>

347
00:23:11,072 --> 00:23:13,632
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - Am I not your son?</font>

348
00:23:14,572 --> 00:23:15,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Why...</font>

349
00:23:16,472 --> 00:23:19,032
<font color=#FFFF00>do you plan to give your fortune to the society...</font>

350
00:23:19,602 --> 00:23:21,702
<font color=#FFFF00>instead of your son?</font>

351
00:23:21,702 --> 00:23:24,232
<font color=#FFFF00>What has the society done for you?</font>

352
00:23:25,302 --> 00:23:27,732
<font color=#FFFF00>None of those who inherited their parents' wealth...</font>

353
00:23:28,172 --> 00:23:29,702
<font color=#FFFF00>led a decent life.</font>

354
00:23:30,372 --> 00:23:31,932
<font color=#FFFF00>None at all.</font>

355
00:23:32,932 --> 00:23:34,232
<font color=#FFFF00>But you were going to leave...</font>

356
00:23:35,132 --> 00:23:38,072
<font color=#FFFF00>- your fortune to Gwang Ho. - Gwang Ho wasn't...</font>

357
00:23:40,802 --> 00:23:43,332
<font color=#FFFF00>greedy like you.</font>

358
00:23:46,232 --> 00:23:47,572
<font color=#FFFF00>He was competent,</font>

359
00:23:48,902 --> 00:23:50,372
<font color=#FFFF00>clever,</font>

360
00:23:51,732 --> 00:23:53,172
<font color=#FFFF00>and modest.</font>

361
00:23:56,702 --> 00:23:58,072
<font color=#FFFF00>Your brother was...</font>

362
00:23:59,172 --> 00:24:00,972
<font color=#FFFF00>a human.</font>

363
00:24:01,872 --> 00:24:03,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you saying...</font>

364
00:24:04,572 --> 00:24:07,672
<font color=#FFFF00>that I'm not a human?</font>

365
00:24:08,532 --> 00:24:11,602
<font color=#FFFF00>You let your brother and his wife die...</font>

366
00:24:11,702 --> 00:24:14,472
<font color=#FFFF00>and tried to take money away from your parents.</font>

367
00:24:15,802 --> 00:24:17,702
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't give you anything, not even a penny.</font>

368
00:24:19,032 --> 00:24:21,172
<font color=#FFFF00>Darn it.</font>

369
00:24:25,332 --> 00:24:26,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

370
00:24:35,032 --> 00:24:37,332
<font color=#FFFF00>You haven't changed at all, Mom.</font>

371
00:24:37,872 --> 00:24:39,572
<font color=#FFFF00>This is too harsh.</font>

372
00:24:39,732 --> 00:24:42,602
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you give your money to someone else other than your son?</font>

373
00:24:42,872 --> 00:24:45,802
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what parents must do, right?</font>

374
00:24:46,072 --> 00:24:47,632
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't bat an eye...</font>

375
00:24:47,802 --> 00:24:49,802
<font color=#FFFF00>about this matter for the last 20 years.</font>

376
00:24:50,502 --> 00:24:52,672
<font color=#FFFF00>You're so merciless.</font>

377
00:24:53,632 --> 00:24:54,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Jeong.</font>

378
00:24:55,932 --> 00:24:57,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Leave her alone.</font>

379
00:24:59,172 --> 00:25:00,972
<font color=#FFFF00>She has nothing to do with this.</font>

380
00:25:02,702 --> 00:25:04,372
<font color=#FFFF00>You already...</font>

381
00:25:05,772 --> 00:25:07,872
<font color=#FFFF00>reported her death, didn't you?</font>

382
00:25:08,672 --> 00:25:09,932
<font color=#FFFF00>You should...</font>

383
00:25:11,372 --> 00:25:14,502
<font color=#FFFF00>give up on your plan to donate your money to the society...</font>

384
00:25:15,532 --> 00:25:17,702
<font color=#FFFF00>and rewrite your will.</font>

385
00:25:18,102 --> 00:25:19,232
<font color=#FFFF00>Or else,</font>

386
00:25:20,172 --> 00:25:21,232
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Jung will...</font>

387
00:25:22,732 --> 00:25:24,732
<font color=#FFFF00>suffer even more.</font>

388
00:25:29,072 --> 00:25:31,502
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm leaving then.</font>

389
00:25:47,902 --> 00:25:50,272
<font color=#FFFF00>- Keep an eye on her. - Yes, sir.</font>

390
00:26:04,302 --> 00:26:05,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go.</font>

391
00:26:25,772 --> 00:26:27,072
<font color=#FFFF00>This is nonsense.</font>

392
00:26:28,102 --> 00:26:29,272
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't believe this.</font>

393
00:26:59,802 --> 00:27:02,432
<font color=#FFFF00>("Romance Learned through Books", Episode 7)</font>

394
00:27:08,372 --> 00:27:09,702
<font color=#FFFF00>(Inbox)</font>

395
00:27:24,002 --> 00:27:25,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Sang Woo.</font>

396
00:27:37,432 --> 00:27:38,572
<font color=#FFFF00>We need to talk.</font>

397
00:27:56,132 --> 00:27:58,072
<font color=#FFFF00>I have no idea what's on your mind.</font>

398
00:27:58,472 --> 00:28:00,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't mind me. Just leave.</font>

399
00:28:02,632 --> 00:28:05,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you kneel down before them? You've done nothing wrong.</font>

400
00:28:05,572 --> 00:28:07,302
<font color=#FFFF00>There's no point in hiding it.</font>

401
00:28:07,332 --> 00:28:08,632
<font color=#FFFF00>They'll find it out in the end.</font>

402
00:28:10,102 --> 00:28:13,432
<font color=#FFFF00>There's no need to make my dad and Jeong Eun suffer too.</font>

403
00:28:14,602 --> 00:28:15,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Myself is enough.</font>

404
00:28:16,272 --> 00:28:17,302
<font color=#FFFF00>So what did they say?</font>

405
00:28:18,002 --> 00:28:20,132
<font color=#FFFF00>What did they tell you when they learned that you're my brother?</font>

406
00:28:21,172 --> 00:28:23,832
<font color=#FFFF00>Didn't they tell you to beg for my mercy?</font>

407
00:28:24,432 --> 00:28:25,872
<font color=#FFFF00>They're not such people.</font>

408
00:28:26,172 --> 00:28:27,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do you have to do this?</font>

409
00:28:28,132 --> 00:28:29,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Because you won't stop.</font>

410
00:28:31,232 --> 00:28:32,532
<font color=#FFFF00>It's undeniable...</font>

411
00:28:32,972 --> 00:28:35,272
<font color=#FFFF00>that they used to be my family.</font>

412
00:28:35,572 --> 00:28:38,332
<font color=#FFFF00>At the same time, it's true that you're my brother.</font>

413
00:28:39,132 --> 00:28:40,172
<font color=#FFFF00>So?</font>

414
00:28:40,732 --> 00:28:44,202
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll straighten out the troubles you caused.</font>

415
00:28:45,402 --> 00:28:46,972
<font color=#FFFF00>If you're done with what you came here for,</font>

416
00:28:47,502 --> 00:28:48,732
