00:55:43,102 --> 00:55:44,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Why didn't you attend the meeting?</font>

836
00:55:45,872 --> 00:55:47,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you have something urgent?</font>

837
00:55:48,202 --> 00:55:49,272
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

838
00:55:49,832 --> 00:55:50,872
<font color=#FFFF00>I was busy.</font>

839
00:55:51,672 --> 00:55:52,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Why?</font>

840
00:55:55,772 --> 00:55:57,502
<font color=#FFFF00>Come sit down and eat.</font>

841
00:55:59,832 --> 00:56:02,202
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not happy with all this.</font>

842
00:56:02,732 --> 00:56:05,032
<font color=#FFFF00>If you don't like to eat with me, I will come back later.</font>

843
00:56:05,102 --> 00:56:07,302
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't need to. Have a seat.</font>

844
00:56:14,072 --> 00:56:16,602
<font color=#FFFF00>So is everything going well with your writing?</font>

845
00:56:17,772 --> 00:56:20,602
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. Thanks to the laptop you gave me,</font>

846
00:56:20,602 --> 00:56:22,702
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm devoting myself to it.</font>

847
00:56:23,572 --> 00:56:25,802
<font color=#FFFF00>But I can't stay here like this.</font>

848
00:56:25,832 --> 00:56:28,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you at least tell me how long I should be here?</font>

849
00:56:33,172 --> 00:56:34,432
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know.</font>

850
00:56:35,272 --> 00:56:37,672
<font color=#FFFF00>It's about time your grandmother showed up.</font>

851
00:56:37,872 --> 00:56:40,202
<font color=#FFFF00>She's coming a little later than I expected.</font>

852
00:56:44,702 --> 00:56:45,972
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm done eating.</font>

853
00:56:47,032 --> 00:56:48,032
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

854
00:57:06,532 --> 00:57:07,602
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with you?</font>

855
00:57:08,272 --> 00:57:10,372
<font color=#FFFF00>What makes you so upset?</font>

856
00:57:10,672 --> 00:57:14,202
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you even care that I'm upset?</font>

857
00:57:14,672 --> 00:57:17,672
<font color=#FFFF00>You just have your own way of doing everything.</font>

858
00:57:17,702 --> 00:57:20,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Can't you see that...</font>

859
00:57:20,972 --> 00:57:23,172
<font color=#FFFF00>everything I do is just for you?</font>

860
00:57:23,402 --> 00:57:25,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that why you rub it in every time?</font>

861
00:57:27,302 --> 00:57:28,772
<font color=#FFFF00>You are doing it for me?</font>

862
00:57:30,002 --> 00:57:32,502
<font color=#FFFF00>You are doing things just to satisfy your selfish desires.</font>

863
00:57:33,772 --> 00:57:34,832
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you say?</font>

864
00:57:38,802 --> 00:57:40,472
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I'm a fool?</font>

865
00:57:40,902 --> 00:57:42,072
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

866
00:57:42,172 --> 00:57:44,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I was born yesterday?</font>

867
00:57:44,202 --> 00:57:47,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I don't know anything about your scheme?</font>

868
00:57:48,472 --> 00:57:51,302
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you talking about?</font>

869
00:57:51,702 --> 00:57:52,802
<font color=#FFFF00>How...</font>

870
00:57:53,332 --> 00:57:56,772
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you lock up your mother as her son?</font>

871
00:57:58,232 --> 00:58:01,102
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you do that to her for 20 years?</font>

872
00:58:03,272 --> 00:58:05,272
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you force her into exile deep in the mountains...</font>

873
00:58:05,272 --> 00:58:06,972
<font color=#FFFF00>as if she was dead?</font>

874
00:58:08,232 --> 00:58:09,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you call yourself a son?</font>

875
00:58:10,232 --> 00:58:12,832
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think it is something a human can do?</font>

876
00:58:13,632 --> 00:58:14,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

877
00:58:15,672 --> 00:58:17,032
<font color=#FFFF00>How did you know that?</font>

878
00:58:17,172 --> 00:58:19,272
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing all that?</font>

879
00:58:19,602 --> 00:58:22,232
<font color=#FFFF00>What will you get out of all this?</font>

880
00:58:22,272 --> 00:58:24,272
<font color=#FFFF00>This company, this house,</font>

881
00:58:24,302 --> 00:58:26,372
<font color=#FFFF00>and all the fame and fortune you've enjoyed...</font>

882
00:58:27,002 --> 00:58:28,832
<font color=#FFFF00>are yours.</font>

883
00:58:30,072 --> 00:58:32,572
<font color=#FFFF00>What else would you need?</font>

884
00:58:34,332 --> 00:58:35,402
<font color=#FFFF00>You...</font>

885
00:58:36,172 --> 00:58:38,532
<font color=#FFFF00>wouldn't understand a word I say.</font>

886
00:58:39,272 --> 00:58:42,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Like you said, you just think...</font>

887
00:58:42,732 --> 00:58:44,402
<font color=#FFFF00>everything is mine.</font>

888
00:58:45,132 --> 00:58:46,902
<font color=#FFFF00>How foolish you are.</font>

889
00:58:48,632 --> 00:58:50,302
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

890
00:58:51,532 --> 00:58:53,102
<font color=#FFFF00>This company, this house,</font>

891
00:58:53,472 --> 00:58:55,632
<font color=#FFFF00>and all the fame and fortune I've enjoyed.</font>

892
00:58:56,032 --> 00:58:58,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Even the car you are driving.</font>

893
00:58:58,732 --> 00:59:02,202
<font color=#FFFF00>Everything will be gone once your grandmother dies.</font>

894
00:59:02,732 --> 00:59:04,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Everything will be over. Do you understand?</font>

895
00:59:05,372 --> 00:59:06,402
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

896
00:59:06,572 --> 00:59:08,532
<font color=#FFFF00>Your spiteful grandmother...</font>

897
00:59:09,132 --> 00:59:10,932
<font color=#FFFF00>didn't leave anything...</font>

898
00:59:11,602 --> 00:59:13,732
<font color=#FFFF00>for you and me.</font>

899
00:59:14,802 --> 00:59:16,532
<font color=#FFFF00>But we've worked...</font>

900
00:59:16,772 --> 00:59:19,472
<font color=#FFFF00>so hard for this company.</font>

901
00:59:20,602 --> 00:59:22,472
<font color=#FFFF00>We devoted ourselves...</font>

902
00:59:22,572 --> 00:59:24,972
<font color=#FFFF00>to make the company grow.</font>

903
00:59:25,132 --> 00:59:26,402
<font color=#FFFF00>That's no good.</font>

904
00:59:28,172 --> 00:59:30,302
<font color=#FFFF00>We are getting nothing for that.</font>

905
00:59:31,272 --> 00:59:32,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you see it now?</font>

906
00:59:33,872 --> 00:59:36,102
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm doing all this for you.</font>

907
00:59:37,072 --> 00:59:38,732
<font color=#FFFF00>What about Ms. Oh Gui Boon?</font>

908
00:59:38,972 --> 00:59:40,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you looking for her?</font>

909
00:59:41,272 --> 00:59:42,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother is alive.</font>

910
00:59:42,802 --> 00:59:44,602
<font color=#FFFF00>You can persuade her.</font>

911
00:59:44,902 --> 00:59:47,732
<font color=#FFFF00>She will recognize our hard work.</font>

912
00:59:49,032 --> 00:59:50,602
<font color=#FFFF00>You have no idea...</font>

913
00:59:51,102 --> 00:59:52,772
<font color=#FFFF00>what kind of person your grandmother is.</font>

914
00:59:53,532 --> 00:59:54,702
<font color=#FFFF00>She will...</font>

915
00:59:55,672 --> 00:59:57,772
<font color=#FFFF00>never redo her will.</font>

916
00:59:57,872 --> 00:59:59,702
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I need Gui Boon.</font>

917
01:00:00,402 --> 01:00:03,372
<font color=#FFFF00>No. I need Hyun Jeong who's been taken care of by Gui Boon.</font>

918
01:00:04,302 --> 01:00:06,972
<font color=#FFFF00>What? What does that mean?</font>

919
01:00:08,102 --> 01:00:10,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you understand?</font>

920
01:00:12,732 --> 01:00:14,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui in that room.</font>

921
01:00:15,772 --> 01:00:17,202
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui is...</font>

922
01:00:18,772 --> 01:00:19,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Bang Hyun Jeong.</font>

923
01:00:30,172 --> 01:00:33,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Darn it. I don't want to eat with her either.</font>

924
01:00:33,532 --> 01:00:35,302
<font color=#FFFF00>What a brat.</font>

925
01:00:43,902 --> 01:00:46,702
<font color=#FFFF00>It's almost over.</font>

926
01:00:47,102 --> 01:00:48,372
<font color=#FFFF00>As soon as...</font>

927
01:00:49,872 --> 01:00:52,232
<font color=#FFFF00>Gui Boon comes here with the key to the safe,</font>

928
01:00:52,232 --> 01:00:53,272
<font color=#FFFF00>it will be over.</font>

929
01:00:53,972 --> 01:00:57,432
<font color=#FFFF00>All you need to do is sit and watch.</font>

930
01:01:32,272 --> 01:01:33,532
<font color=#FFFF00>Chairwoman Park.</font>

931
01:01:34,402 --> 01:01:36,502
<font color=#FFFF00>What should I do now?</font>

932
01:01:37,872 --> 01:01:38,902
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry,</font>

933
01:01:39,572 --> 01:01:43,272
<font color=#FFFF00>but I have no choice for my poor Dong Hui.</font>

934
01:01:45,032 --> 01:01:47,032
<font color=#FFFF00>I never thought it'd end up like this.</font>

935
01:01:47,902 --> 01:01:49,732
<font color=#FFFF00>Decades of work...</font>

936
01:01:50,172 --> 01:01:52,232
<font color=#FFFF00>is going down the drain.</font>

937
01:01:55,672 --> 01:01:57,102
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

938
01:02:19,232 --> 01:02:20,272
<font color=#FFFF00>So you mean...</font>

939
01:02:21,432 --> 01:02:23,372
<font color=#FFFF00>there's no way, right?</font>

940
01:02:25,272 --> 01:02:26,402
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

941
01:02:27,772 --> 01:02:28,802
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's sell it.</font>

942
01:02:30,932 --> 01:02:31,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry?</font>

943
01:02:33,172 --> 01:02:34,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's sell this house.</font>

944
01:02:35,472 --> 01:02:36,532
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother.</font>

945
01:02:38,732 --> 01:02:40,572
<font color=#FFFF00>This house means a lot to you.</font>

946
01:02:41,972 --> 01:02:44,632
<font color=#FFFF00>You built it with the money your parents left to you.</font>

947
01:02:44,802 --> 01:02:46,502
<font color=#FFFF00>You gave birth to Hyung Seop,</font>

948
01:02:46,602 --> 01:02:48,472
<font color=#FFFF00>raised him, and married him off in this house.</font>

949
01:02:48,732 --> 01:02:49,972
<font color=#FFFF00>This is where...</font>

950
01:02:50,232 --> 01:02:52,632
<font color=#FFFF00>your grandchildren and great-grandchildren were born.</font>

951
01:02:53,172 --> 01:02:55,772
<font color=#FFFF00>I should save my kids first.</font>

952
01:02:56,602 --> 01:02:59,332
<font color=#FFFF00>They're having such a hard time.</font>

953
01:02:59,332 --> 01:03:02,772
<font color=#FFFF00>This house means nothing when my kids are suffering.</font>

954
01:03:04,702 --> 01:03:05,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

955
01:03:07,532 --> 01:03:08,702
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

956
01:03:10,272 --> 01:03:11,602
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

957
01:03:13,402 --> 01:03:14,502
<font color=#FFFF00>My house...</font>

958
01:03:16,432 --> 01:03:19,472
<font color=#FFFF00>doesn't have to be this building.</font>

959
01:03:20,932 --> 01:03:21,932
<font color=#FFFF00>The place...</font>

960
01:03:22,502 --> 01:03:24,702
<font color=#FFFF00>in which I can live with my children...</font>

961
01:03:25,372 --> 01:03:27,972
<font color=#FFFF00>is my house.</font>

962
01:03:28,372 --> 01:03:30,972
<font color=#FFFF00>So don't be so sad...</font>

963
01:03:31,272 --> 01:03:32,732
<font color=#FFFF00>about selling this house.</font>

964
01:03:34,502 --> 01:03:36,932
<font color=#FFFF00>It's all my fault.</font>

965
01:03:38,502 --> 01:03:40,032
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry, Mom.</font>

966
01:03:42,002 --> 01:03:45,602
<font color=#FFFF00>You know many things can happen in our life.</font>

967
01:03:48,972 --> 01:03:51,032
<font color=#FFFF00>If we don't want to face rough rides,</font>

968
01:03:52,732 --> 01:03:55,032
<font color=#FFFF00>we should die early.</font>

969
01:03:55,432 --> 01:03:57,032
<font color=#FFFF00>If we don't like that option,</font>

970
01:03:57,332 --> 01:04:00,372
<font color=#FFFF00>we must not have been born.</font>

971
01:04:01,832 --> 01:04:04,332
<font color=#FFFF00>But we were born...</font>

972
01:04:04,402 --> 01:04:05,702
<font color=#FFFF00>and we have to live.</font>

973
01:04:08,732 --> 01:04:10,172
<font color=#FFFF00>We will have...</font>

974
01:04:11,872 --> 01:04:13,902
<font color=#FFFF00>good times again later.</font>

975
01:04:16,972 --> 01:04:18,802
<font color=#FFFF00>So let's just sell this house.</font>

976
01:04:19,732 --> 01:04:22,302
<font color=#FFFF00>If all of us go out and work,</font>

977
01:04:24,732 --> 01:04:27,672
<font color=#FFFF00>we might be able to buy a bigger place someday.</font>

978
01:04:29,702 --> 01:04:30,902
<font color=#FFFF00>So...</font>

979
01:04:31,732 --> 01:04:33,872
<font color=#FFFF00>stop hesitating and just sell this house.</font>

980
01:04:34,672 --> 01:04:36,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, we can't do that.</font>

981
01:04:37,432 --> 01:04:39,072
<font color=#FFFF00>We can't sell this house.</font>

982
01:04:39,372 --> 01:04:42,032
<font color=#FFFF00>We can never do that, Mother.</font>

983
01:04:55,272 --> 01:04:58,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Guys, clean up. Someone wants to look at the house.</font>

984
01:04:59,272 --> 01:05:00,272
<font color=#FFFF00>Who's coming?</font>

985
01:05:00,502 --> 01:05:02,702
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing? We'll have visitors soon.</font>

986
01:05:04,172 --> 01:05:05,432
<font color=#FFFF00>Welcome.</font>

987
01:05:05,772 --> 01:05:08,102
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm happy that someone wants to buy it this quickly.</font>

988
01:05:08,102 --> 01:05:10,632
<font color=#FFFF00>You know the location of this place is really good.</font>

989
01:05:11,272 --> 01:05:12,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Please come in.</font>

990
01:05:19,102 --> 01:05:20,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello.</font>

991
01:05:31,632 --> 01:05:32,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

992
01:05:58,572 --> 01:06:00,232
<font color=#FFFF00>(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

993
01:06:00,902 --> 01:06:02,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Get out. Get out now!</font>

994
01:06:03,432 --> 01:06:06,272
<font color=#FFFF00>I need you to move out in few days.</font>

995
01:06:06,332 --> 01:06:07,332
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry?</font>

996
01:06:07,632 --> 01:06:09,402
<font color=#FFFF00>What's all this?</font>

997
01:06:09,972 --> 01:06:12,872
<font color=#FFFF00>- What on earth is going on? - Gui Boon.</font>

998
01:06:13,902 --> 01:06:15,772
<font color=#FFFF00>- He got a loan? - Hey.</font>

999
01:06:16,002 --> 01:06:18,072
<font color=#FFFF00>Go get Han Seong Hoon!</font>

1000
01:06:18,532 --> 01:06:20,402
<font color=#FFFF00>We'd better not let Dong Hui...</font>

1001
01:06:20,772 --> 01:06:22,032
<font color=#FFFF00>know all this.</font>

1002
01:06:22,032 --> 01:06:23,032
<font color=#FFFF00>(DNA test results)</font>

1003
01:06:23,302 --> 01:06:24,332
<font color=#FFFF00>My name...</font>

1004
01:06:25,332 --> 01:06:26,332
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

